text: Yakhin () is a Tatar masculine surname originating from the Arabic given name Yahya, its feminine counterpart is Yakhina. It may refer to: *Alexei Yakhin (born 1984), Russian ice hockey goaltender *Guzel Yakhina (born 1977), Russian author and screenwriter *Röstäm Yaxin (1921–1993), Tatar composer and pianist ==References== Category:Tatar-language surnames
title: Yakhin
